snippet.title: Launch Trailer | Warhammer Age of Sigmar: Realms of Ruin
snippet.description:
Available now: https://www.aosrealmsofruin.com/buy

Lead your faction into brutal strategic combat in Warhammer Age of Sigmar: Realms of Ruin! Coming to PC, PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X|S on 17 November.

Join the Discord: https://discord.gg/realmsofruin

Follow us on:

Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/frontier
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RealmsOfRuin
Facebook: https://facebook.com/PlayRealmsOfRuin
Instagram: https://instagram.com/RealmsOfRuin
